{"id": 58368, "date": "2025-08-11T04:00:26", "date_gmt": "2025-08-11T11:00:26", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=58368"}, "modified": "2026-06-01T15:26:21", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-01T22:26:21", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-11-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/11/kingdom-of-days-august-11-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 11"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1972: </strong>Bruce plays his third of six two-shows-a-night solo gigs at Max&#8217;s Kansas City that week.</p>\n<p><strong>1974</strong>:\u00a0Bruce cancels a gig at the Cambridge Performance Center to make room for <em>Born to Run\u00a0</em>recording sessions.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11965\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-08-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?fit=290%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"290,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-08-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?fit=290%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11965 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?resize=290%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"290\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?w=290&amp;ssl=1 290w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?resize=174%2C300&amp;ssl=1 174w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session for his upcoming album at Atlantic Studios in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the River Tour to Detroit&#8217;s Joe Louis Arena for the first of two nights.</p>\n<div id=\"v-j4p8FdMJ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/j4p8FdMJ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20303\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-08-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?fit=2080%2C799&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2080,799\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-08-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?fit=758%2C291&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20303 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=758%2C291&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?w=2080&amp;ssl=1 2080w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=300%2C115&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=1024%2C393&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=768%2C295&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=1536%2C590&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-08-11.png?resize=2048%2C787&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At Night Five (of ten) at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford, John Entwistle guest-stars on the show-closing &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-D7LMS4B8-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/D7LMS4B8?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1985: </strong>At Pittsburgh&#8217;s Three Rivers Stadium, Nils and Roy miss their signal to take the stage, so Bruce starts the show and plays &#8220;Born in the U.S.A.&#8221; without them. Bruce will do a pre-show headcount ever after.</p>\n<div id=\"v-LBLlimMh-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/LBLlimMh?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28605\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-11a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?fit=1948%2C2052&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1948,2052\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-08-11a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?fit=758%2C799&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28605 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=758%2C798&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"798\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?w=1948&amp;ssl=1 1948w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=285%2C300&amp;ssl=1 285w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=972%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 972w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=768%2C809&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=1458%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1458w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?resize=1944%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1944w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-11a.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise guest appearance at the Garden State Arts Center in Holmdel, joining Ringo Starr and His All Starr Band (including Nils and Clarence) for the encores of &#8220;Get Back,&#8221; &#8220;Long Tall Sally,&#8221; &#8220;Photograph&#8221; and &#8220;With a Little Help From My Friends.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OK-lSq3vVZ0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EzxoTbt0FRU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vqMxTWqVoYM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20304\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-08-11a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?fit=892%2C901&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"892,901\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-08-11a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?fit=758%2C766&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20304 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?resize=758%2C766&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"766\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?w=892&amp;ssl=1 892w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?resize=297%2C300&amp;ssl=1 297w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?resize=768%2C776&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11a.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20305\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-08-11b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?fit=1128%2C1125&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1128,1125\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-08-11b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?fit=758%2C756&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20305 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=758%2C756&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"756\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?w=1128&amp;ssl=1 1128w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=1024%2C1021&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=768%2C766&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=550%2C550&amp;ssl=1 550w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1989-08-11b.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>It&#8217;s the penultimate show of Bruce and the E Street Band&#8217;s fifteen-night Reunion Tour stand at East Rutherford&#8217;s Continental Airlines Arena, and the show rockets out of the gate with the first performance of &#8220;Night&#8221; in fifteen years. Later in the show: the first &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221; in 24 years, and the show-closing tour premiere of &#8220;4th of July, Asbury Park (Sandy).&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-a9oVxoDc-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/a9oVxoDc?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/O5iFPH6aig0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-bAJmbbez-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/bAJmbbez?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their three-show Rising stand at Philadelphia&#8217;s Lincoln Financial Field in peak form, opening with &#8220;From Small Things (Big Things One Day Come),&#8221; and tour premiering &#8220;I&#8217;m Goin&#8217; Down&#8221; and &#8220;Pretty Flamingo&#8221; (the latter of which hadn&#8217;t been played in 25 years). Throw in a rare &#8220;Incident on 57th Street&#8221; &#8220;Be True,&#8221; and a show-closing &#8220;I&#8217;m a Rocker,&#8221; and you&#8217;ve got the makings of a killer setlist. And then there&#8217;s that &#8220;Ramrod&#8221; under a full moon&#8230;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DyPmTlgg180?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wgoIynLqGT8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RieYi5kFOeE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-BhBwRNao-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/BhBwRNao?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ItDtlDPy-nE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDItDtlDPy-nE\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce continues his solo acoustic swing through the Pacific Northwest with a show at Seattle&#8217;s Key Arena, where Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Be True&#8221; and plays a one-off guitar version of &#8220;For You.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DOr0YpxkVtI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ee2uF3Sun5c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WUMuta55JIg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two shows at Wrigley Field in Chicago.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tDV7mychhkw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;start=99&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>It&#8217;s a day of long-awaited returns, as Bruce brings back &#8220;Pretty Flamingo,&#8221; &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221; and &#8220;Night&#8221; after many years of absence. Plus: The Rising hits the top of the album chart, Bruce makes a guest appearance with Ringo Starr and His All Starr Band, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 53996, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [236, 558, 534, 41, 783, 610, 561, 834, 60, 1435, 173, 630, 650, 286, 826,