ocals in Montana when he jams with a restaurant house band, and shocks fans worldwide when Springsteen on Broadway is officially confirmed. Plus: Joe Grushecky catches his first Bruce concert, the Springsteen/Appel lawsuit gets underway, and Bruce plays his legendary Darkness Show at The Agora.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-Summertime-Blues-mp3-image.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-Summertime-Blues-mp3-image.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-Summertime-Blues-mp3-image.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-Summertime-Blues-mp3-image.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-Summertime-Blues-mp3-image.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57811, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/23/kingdom-of-days-july-23-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 58368, "position": 3}, "title": "July 23", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 23, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Don't even know where to start today--treasures abound. Listen to a gorgeous Bruce Springsteen Band performance from '71, the earliest known performance of \"New York City Serenade,\" watch a delightful Copenhagen street performance, and so very much more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/19710723_2_front.jpg?fit=980%2C943&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/19710723_2_front.jpg?fit=980%2C943&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/19710723_2_front.jpg?fit=980%2C943&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/19710723_2_front.jpg?fit=980%2C943&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57749, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/18/kingdom-of-days-july-18-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 58368, "position": 4}, "title": "July 18", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 18, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce makes a surprise \"guest\" appearance with Joe Grushecky (if 15 of 18 songs can be considered a guest appearance), Bruce teases an injured Jake, the Devils and Dust Tour set list busts open, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/19990718.jpeg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/19990718.jpeg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/19990718.jpeg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/19990718.jpeg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/19990718.jpeg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 59507, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/30/kingdom-of-days-august-30-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 58368, "position": 5}, "